exists.name: exists
exists.short_desc: Determine if a file or directory exists.

get.name: get
get.short_desc: Get the contents of a file.

sharedGet.name: sharedGet
sharedGet.short_desc: Get contents of a file with shared access.

getRequire.name: getRequire
getRequire.short_desc: Get the returned value of a file.

hash.name: hash
hash.short_desc: Get the MD5 hash of the file at the given path.

put.name: put
put.short_desc: Write the contents of a file.

replace.name: replace
replace.short_desc: Write the contents of a file, replacing it atomically if it already exists.

chmod.name: chmod
chmod.short_desc: Get or set UNIX mode of a file or directory.

delete.name: delete
delete.short_desc: Delete the file at a given path.

move.name: move
move.short_desc: Move a file to a new location.

copy.name: copy
copy.short_desc: Copy a file to a new location.

link.name: link
link.short_desc: Create a hard link to the target file or directory.

name.name: name
name.short_desc: Extract the file name from a file path.

basename.name: basename
basename.short_desc: Extract the trailing name component from a file path.

dirname.name: dirname
dirname.short_desc: Extract the parent directory from a file path.

extension.name: extension
extension.short_desc: Extract the file extension from a file path.

type.name: type
type.short_desc: Get the file type of a given file.

mimeType.name: mimeType
mimeType.short_desc: Get the mime-type of a given file.

size.name: size
size.short_desc: Get the file size of a given file.

lastModified.name: lastModified
lastModified.short_desc: Get the file's last modification time.

isDirectory.name: isDirectory
isDirectory.short_desc: Determine if the given path is a directory.

isReadable.name: isReadable
isReadable.short_desc: Determine if the given path is readable.

isWritable.name: isWritable
isWritable.short_desc: Determine if the given path is writable.

isFile.name: isFile
isFile.short_desc: Determine if the given path is a file.

glob.name: glob
glob.short_desc: Find path names matching a given pattern.

files.name: files
files.short_desc: Get an array of all files in a directory.

allFiles.name: allFiles
allFiles.short_desc: Get all of the files from the given directory (recursive).

directories.name: directories
directories.short_desc: Get all of the directories within a given directory.

copyDirectory.name: copyDirectory
copyDirectory.short_desc: Copy a directory from one location to another.

deleteDirectory.name: deleteDirectory
deleteDirectory.long_desc: The directory itself may be optionally preserved.

deleteDirectories.name: deleteDirectories
deleteDirectories.short_desc: Remove all of the directories within a given directory.

cleanDirectory.name: cleanDirectory
cleanDirectory.short_desc: Empty the specified directory of all files and folders.

mixin.name: mixin
mixin.short_desc: Mix another object into the class.
